OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA pleasant
OL,6,Fevening with widespread sunshine and
OL,7,Feasing winds for many, followed by a
OL,8,Fmostly clear and cool night, with a
OL,9,Flittle patchy cloud during the early
OL,10,Fhours. Remaining breezy along coasts.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FPartly cloudy through the
OL,13,Fmorning on Friday, though with some
OL,14,Fsunny intervals. Clouding over late
OL,15,Fafternoon into the evening with the
OL,16,Fpossibility of some light rain for a
OL,17,Ftime.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
